<% provide(:title, "Contact") %>

<h1 class="fw-light">Contact Us</h1>

<div class="text-muted">

  <p>
    We’d love to hear from you. Whether you have questions, feedback, or suggestions,
    your input helps us improve <strong>StudyMates</strong> for everyone.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>General Inquiries</h5>
  <p>
    For general questions, suggestions, or collaboration inquiries, you can reach us at:
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Email:</strong>
    <a href="mailto:support@studymates.app" class="text-dark">
      support@studymates.app
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>
    We aim to respond within 24–48 hours.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>Technical Support</h5>
  <p>
    If you encounter bugs, errors, or unexpected behavior, please report them through our
    <a href="https://github.com/ycisir/study_mates/issues" target="_blank" class="text-dark">
      GitHub Issues page
    </a>.
  </p>

  <p>When submitting an issue, please include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A clear description of the issue</li>
    <li>Steps to reproduce the problem</li>
    <li>Expected vs actual behavior</li>
    <li>Screenshots or screen recordings (if applicable)</li>
    <li>Browser and device details</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h5>Feature Requests</h5>
  <p>
    We welcome ideas and suggestions for improving StudyMates. Your feedback helps shape the future of the platform.
  </p>

  <p>
    You can also connect with us via
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ycisir/" target="_blank" class="text-dark">LinkedIn</a>.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>Response Time</h5>
  <p>
    Most inquiries are answered within 24–48 hours. Critical issues are prioritized.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <p class="mb-0">
    Thank you for being part of the StudyMates community.
  </p>

</div>